observations.recommendation:
We recommended that Management:
a) Direct the Municipal Accountant to stop the recording of collections from sale of bid documents to Miscellaneous Income, and henceforth, record the collections to its proper account as Trust Liability and ensure that the payments of BAC and TWG honoraria are duly supported with the required documents to include the list of completed procurement projects together with the Notice of Award of each project;
c) Revert the appropriated amount of ₱500,000.00 and sourced the BAC honorarium payment from the Municipality’s savings.
